text: Did you see a preview of any of the creatures?
Ok, so there are bird like ones, fish ones, and little bug guys with wings on their back and lots of legs
All of the bird ones are wudsy no matter what colors they are
If you see a fish with a green body (the color of the stripes doesn't matter), it's wudsy
And wudsy bugs have green wings on their back, the color of their body doesn't matter
Okay, so all of the bird ones, the fish with green bodies, and the bugs with green wings
No problem! Hope that was clear enough so it all makes sense when you see them
